188 Section 2. Section 32-6-19.1 is added to Division 1 of
189 Article 1 of Chapter 6 of Title 32 of the Code of Alabama
190 1975, to read as follows:
191 §32-6-19.1
192 (a) Except as provided in subsection (b), a motor
193 vehicle impounded pursuant to Section 32-6-19 may be redeemed
194 and released from impoundment upon the occurrence of all of
195 the following:
196 (1) The registered owner, or the owner's representative
